data.description: A unique opportunity to create your dream home, within a charming community brimming with exciting amenities, including a playground, basketball court, and a sparkling pool. This 3-bed, 2.5-bath gem is the perfect blend of charm and modern convenience. The kitchen is adorned with Victorian crown molding, granite countertops, and a matching backsplash, along with high-end Samsung appliances. There's a versatile converted patio space, perfect for a playroom or additional bedroom. The primary suite boasts a spacious walk-in closet with built-in shelving. You'll also appreciate the one-car garage, a 2016-installed roof, hurricane shutters, and ample storage throughout. This is more than just a home; it's a welcoming community that promises a life of comfort, style, and endless opportunities.
